description:
The Father is Lord, and what does that mean? He is just and holy, merciful, gracious, slow to anger, abounding in steadfast love and faithfulness. But how do we talk about Him when He feels so distant? Find out more in this episode.


#Adventistbeliefs

To watch the full episode, paste the link into your browser: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vCP1rNKD2rs
